  "body": "### Description\nTransition at TTD to the merge consensus mechanism is a critical point and is likely to be encounter edge and adversarial cases.  Besu needs comprehensive coverage of the transition and reorg cases as it relates to TTD. \n\nFor more detail see:\n\nhttps://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-3675#terminal-total-difficulty-vs-block-number\n\n### Acceptance Criteria\nminimally, integration test cases for\n* nominal transition at TTD\n* reorg post-TTD but pre-first finalized block / call to engine_forkChoiceUpdated\n* attempted post-TTD reorg, post first finalized block\n",
